text.section:
In addition to the jurisdiction specified in Subtitle 8A of this title, the court has exclusive original jurisdiction over:
Voluntary placement hearings;
Proceedings arising from a petition alleging that a child is a CINA;
Proceedings arising under the Interstate Compact on the Placement of Children;
Proceedings to terminate parental rights after a CINA proceeding;
Guardianship review proceedings after a TPR proceeding; and
Adoption proceedings, if any, after a TPR proceeding.
